AI DevOps Auto-Healing Platform (AIOps)
A production-grade DevOps automation platform that integrates CI/CD, container orchestration, observability, centralized logging, AI-driven anomaly detection, and automated remediation to build a self-healing cloud infrastructure.

This platform automates the entire software lifecycle including build, deployment, monitoring, log analysis, and automated recovery.

Platform Capabilities

• Continuous Integration & Continuous Deployment
• Containerized application infrastructure
• Kubernetes cluster orchestration
• Infrastructure monitoring & observability
• Centralized log aggregation
• AI-based anomaly detection
• Automated infrastructure recovery

